Framework layers like js.schtml, jetty.schtml are marked with compiledOnly and so are never dynamic.

To run from the IDE, specify the example layer name as either compiled or dynamic. 
include all layers on one line as either compiled or dynamic layers.

To run from the command line, run "scc layer1 layer2", for compiled execution and 'scc -dyn layer1 layer' for dynamic. 

Add the -v option to see the compiled set of layers and track build progress.

Add -a to rebuild from scratch.

